__section__
default
__description__
Prints the bar above each story, containing the actual title of the story.

* width = width of widget
* title = text for title
* future = boolean: whether story is in the future
	(currently not used)
* td_extra = extra_table cell(s) and contents to include after after the title table-cell

__title__

__page__
misc
__lang__
en_US
__name__
titlebar
__template__

[% future = 0 %]
[% IF future %]
<div class="future">
[% END %]
<div class="generaltitle">
	<div class="title">
		<h3>
			[% title %]
		</h3>
	</div>
</div>
[% IF future %]
</div>
[% END %]

__seclev__
10000
__version__
$Id$
